Network Video Recorders




Versatile and Scalable Solutions for Use in Finance and Banking, Retail, and Other Enterprise ApplicationsVerint EdgeVMS is an enterprise NVR management and situation awareness platform which brings together Verint's world-class NVR solution, Verint EdgeVR, with critical software packages for video viewing and automated monitoring. Verint EdgeVMS features industry-leading security and business system integrations and is a powerful solution designed for long life and low cost of ownership.

   

Verint EdgeVR - Hybrid Analog/IP Network Video RecorderEnterprise-class, IP-based network video recorder for large-scale, geographically distributed operations, with hybrid analog/IP capabilities, and industry-leading security and business system interfaces.Portfolio includes:Verint EdgeVR 300 IP-based, with hybrid analog/IP option and support for up to 64 cameras (includes analog, IP and megapixel cameras)Verint EdgeVR 40 IP-based, with hybrid analog/IP option and support for up to 12 cameras (includes analog, IP and megapixel cameras) and optional PoE optionSee Details Verint



Verint EdgeVMS Vid-Center – Video Viewing SoftwareA unified video viewing interface for banking organizations, with up to 32 camera views per screen and user-defined virtual NVRs, NVR groups, zone views, and guard tours. Verint EdgeVMS Vid-CenterSee Details 



Verint EdgeVMS Op-Center – Enterprise Management SoftwareRemote and centralized enterprise management software for the suite of Verint NVRs, including EdgeVR, NetDVR II, MicroDVR II and legacy systems. Verint EdgeVMS Op-Center See Details 









   



    



