IP Cameras




Verint helps organizations address the challenges of indoor and outdoor video surveillance with a wide array of powerful IP cameras that accommodate a variety of objectives and budgets.Verint IP cameras deliver high-definition video up to 5 megapixels in resolution. Multi-streaming enables users to customize H.264, MPEG-4, or MJPEG compression formats to meet their video surveillance requirements. Verint IP cameras combine excellent video quality with ultra-efficient bandwidth management and come in a variety of form factors — from fixed body and pan/tilt/zoom cameras to indoor and all-weather IP domes — to accommodate virtually any video surveillance application. V5620PTZ Series V5620PTZ-18ID-CIP PTZ INDOOR CAMERA V5620PTZ-18DW-CIP PTZ OUTDOOR CAMERA 1080p 2MP high definition resolutionRobust PTZ platform18X optical zoom for amazing image capture capabilityS5250 Series S5250BX-DNIP BOX S5250FD-DNFIXED DOME S5250FDW-DNVANDAL DOME 5 megapixelH.264 compressionDome features 3-axisGimbal and remote focus & zoomMultiple mounting optionsEasy-to-install designS5120 Series S5120BX-DNIP BOX S5120FD-DNINDOOR DOME S5120FDW-DNVANDAL DOME 2 megapixelH.264 compressionDome features 3-axisGimbal and remote focus & zoomMultiple mounting optionsEasy-to-install designVerint Height Strip and Miniature Wide Dynamic Range Cameras IP Height StripCamera Miniature Wide Dynamic Range Camera High PerformancePower over EthernetDiscreet designFlexible installation options































































 



 







